                     alt="Photo of customer Abhay"
                     src="~/img/Updated Logo/Customer2.png" />
                <blockquote class="testimonial-text">
                    I love this eBook website! It's easy to use, has a wide range of books, and the download process is hassle-free. The customer service is also commendable. They were quick to respond and very helpful when I had an issue. I highly recommend this site to all eBook readers.

                </blockquote>
                <p class="testimonial-name">&mdash; Abhay</p>
            </figure>

            <figure class="testimonial">
                <img class="testimonial-img"
                     alt="Photo of customer Dhileep"
                     src="~/img/Updated Logo/Customer1.png" />
