                </blockquote>
                <p class="testimonial-name">&mdash; Sanjay </p>
            </figure>

            <figure class="testimonial">
                <img class="testimonial-img"
                     alt="Photo of customer Soham"
                     src="~/img/Updated Logo/Customer6.png" />
                <blockquote class="testimonial-text">
                    I got Book Dash for the whole family, and it frees up so much
                    time! Plus, there is a wide range of books to go through.
                </blockquote>
                <p class="testimonial-name">&mdash; Soham</p>
